Property.valueExpression:
SELECT DISTINCT CAST(T1.STDRD_YM AS INT)                                                                                                 AS 기준년월
     , CAST(SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,1,4)||CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,5,2) IN ('01','02','03') THEN '01'
                                          WHEN SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,5,2) IN ('04','05','06') THEN '02'
                                          WHEN SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,5,2) IN ('07','08','09') THEN '03'
                                          WHEN SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,5,2) IN ('10','11','12') THEN '04'
                                     END  AS INT)                                                                                        AS 기준분기
     , CAST(SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,1,4)||CASE WHEN SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,5,2) IN ('01','02','03','04','05','06') THEN '01'
                                          WHEN SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,5,2) IN ('07','08','09','10','11','12') THEN '02'
                                     END  AS INT)                                                                                        AS 기준반기
     , CAST(SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM ,1,4) AS INT)                                                                                             AS 기준년도
     , SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,5,2)||'월'                                                                                                     AS 월명
     , CAST(TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(T1.STDRD_YMD,'YYYYMMDD') + INTERVAL '-1 MONTH','YYYYMM') AS INTEGER)                                         AS 전월
     , SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,1,4)||'년'                                                                                                     AS 년도명
     , CAST(TO_CHAR(LAST_DAY(TO_DATE(T1.STDRD_YMD,'YYYYMMDD')),'DD') AS SMALLINT)                                                        AS 기준일수
     , CAST(SUBSTR(TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(T1.STDRD_YM,'YYYYMM') +  INTERVAL '-1 YEAR','YYYYMMDD'),1,6) AS INT)                                  AS 전년동월기준년월
     , CAST(LAST_DAY(TO_DATE(T1.STDRD_YM,'YYYYMM')) - TO_DATE(SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YMD,1,4)||'0101','YYYYMMDD') + 1  AS SMALLINT)             AS 년누적일수
     , CAST(LAST_DAY(TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(T1.STDRD_YM,'YYYYMM') +  INTERVAL '-1 YEAR','YYYYMMDD'),'YYYYMMDD'))
       -  TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(SUBSTR(T1.STDRD_YM,1,4)||'0101','YYYYMMDD') +  INTERVAL '-1 YEAR','YYYYMMDD'),'YYYYMMDD') AS SMALLINT) AS 전년동월누적일수
  FROM WCM_CAL_M AS T1  /* CM_달력마스터 */
